INSERT INTO `wp_animalhealth_posts` VALUES (51,1,'2013-04-03 23:19:23','2013-04-03 23:19:23','<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1002A-2 oz. Spray and 1008A-8 oz. Spray</span></strong>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nCatalog No. 1002A and 1008A\r\nCase Quantity: 2 oz : 24   /   8 oz : 12\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h4>Lasts for hours! Extraordinary odor eliminating capability. Leaves a squeaky clean background smell.</h4>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nEven small animals can create big odors. Animal waste odors are some of the most stubborn smells to eliminate. Even a small “accident” can foul an entire house with an embarrassing odor. Sani-Zone™ is the most effective way to get rid of those nasty odors in the air, in carpet, upholstery and litter boxes.\r\nSani-Zone Effectively eliminates odors from anal gland secretion, tom cat spray, necrotic tissue, urine, feces, emesis, etc. Sani-Zone chemically and instantly cancels animal odors without masking.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.anacapa-tech.net/animalhealth/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Cat-with-flowers.png\"><img class=\"alignright  wp-image-130\" alt=\"Cat with flowers\" src=\"http://www.anacapa-tech.net/animalhealth/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Cat-with-flowers-300x300.png\" /></a>Spray directly toward the source of the odor or use as an air freshener; one or two sprays in an average size room eliminates odors and leaves a squeaky clean fragrance that lasts for hours.\r\n<h4>Directions for Use</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Spray directly toward the source of the odor or use as an air freshener; one or\r\ntwo sprays in an average size room eliminates odors and leaves a squeaky clean fragrance that lasts for hours.</li>\r\n	<li>Do not spray directly on to people or pets.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.anacapa-tech.net/animalhealth/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/msds-sani-zone-maximum-strength-odor-eliminator.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1027\" alt=\"images\" src=\"http://www.anacapa-tech.net/live/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/images.jpeg\" />Material Safety Data Sheet - Sani-Zone Air Freshener</a>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.anacapa-tech.net/live/wp-content/uploads/2010/01/Sani-zone-general-trifold5.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1027\" alt=\"images\" src=\"http://www.anacapa-tech.net/live/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/images.jpeg\" />Sani-Zone Brochure</a>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1027\" alt=\"images\" src=\" http://www.anacapa-tech.net/animalhealth/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/OrderNowIcon-blue-e1392395879359.png\" /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://www.anacapa-tech.net/animalhealth/ordering-information-2 /\">Order Sani-Zone™ 2 oz. or 8 oz.</a></span></h2>','Sani-Zone<sup>™</sup> Odor Eliminator','An extremely effective odor eliminator','publish','closed','closed','','sani-zone','','','2014-05-08 23:01:13','2014-05-08 23:01:13','',0,'http://animalhealth.anacapa-tech.dev/?post_type=product&#038;p=51',2,'product','',0);
